}}'''耳炎'''（英文：Otitis），是指[[耳朵|耳朵]]受到感染而引发[[炎症|炎症]]，在人和其他动物身上均可发生。耳炎有[[急性|急性]]和[[慢性病|慢性]]两种。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Otitis: MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia|url=https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/001336.htm|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=medlineplus.gov|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426171911/https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/001336.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

按发炎部位，耳炎可细分为：

* [[外耳炎|'''外耳炎''']]，又称“游泳耳”，是指外耳或[[耳道|耳道]]发炎，多为[[细菌|细菌]]感染，触碰或拉扯耳部会产生疼痛。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Swimmer's ear - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/swimmers-ear/symptoms-causes/syc-20351682|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503135127/https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/swimmers-ear/symptoms-causes/syc-20351682|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[中耳炎|'''中耳炎''']]，是指[[中耳|中耳]]发炎。中耳炎中，[[鼓膜|鼓膜]]后的[[鼓室|鼓室]]中可因为发炎而出现液体堵塞（积水）。中耳炎属于儿童的常见病，有时需要进行{{link-en|鼓膜切开术|Myringotomy}}进行治疗。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ear infection (middle ear) - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/ear-infections/symptoms-causes/syc-20351616|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507002515/https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/ear-infections/symptoms-causes/syc-20351616|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''[[内耳炎|内耳炎]]，'''又称[[迷路炎|迷路炎]]，是指内耳发炎，多为[[病毒|病毒]]感染。 由于内耳中存在[[听觉|听觉]]及[[平衡觉|平衡觉]]的感受器，故内耳感染可造成[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]和[[听觉障碍|听觉障碍]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Otitis Interna - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/immunology-and-microbiology/otitis-interna|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=Science Direct}}</ref>

